cast.overview: Two young officers are marked for death after confiscating a small cache of money and firearms from the members of a notorious cartel during a routine traffic stop.
cast.title: End of Watch

details.biography: Kristy Wu (born October 11, 1982) is an American actress. On television, she starred in Flight 29 Down (2005 - 2007) and had recurring roles in the seventh season of Buffy the Vampire Slayer (2003), the third season of The Legend of Korra (2014), and the first two seasons of Transformers: Robots in Disguise (2015 - 2016). Her film appearances include Cry Wolf (2005), Return to Halloweentown (2006), and End of Watch (2012).
details.name: Kristy Wu
